ike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:59:39.000Z","msg":"可能後天弱智<br />\n又靚又弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bddadd7a669764098c1b8aa4177e1974d26b16b","tid":1180430,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ff41eefe544bdbf1da68ad91e63065ffbf2b6f","tid":1180430,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f689c52c3e5e450037b8804fdaa65837c80ee2","tid":1180430,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:04:38.000Z","msg":"嘉恩原來到了藍田找男友，但男友只給了少量現金予她便離開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n少到返唔到屋企?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:12:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"社工：社交技巧較弱　易投入感情<br />\n<br />\n有資深社工指出，輕度智障或邊緣智力的青少年，如同一般人一樣有情感需要，踏入青春期會渴望「拍拖」，又希望有人關心。由於身邊人或家人不理解他們，他們缺乏情感支援網絡，當有其他人加以關心時，他們沒有分辨善惡，且社交技巧較弱，容易投入感情，分不清楚是友情抑或愛惰，最終墮入陷阱，被人騙財甚至騙色，故不少家長擔心子女被人欺騙，而阻止他們發展感情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到單野個男友錯咁<br />\n明明係男友搵番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd13ccf0e3d245585044ceed6346cf322a61716","tid":1180430,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:29:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為係唐氏果類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cbcf3362878d893ebcd81303a271db74e0377b","tid":1180430,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:36:05.000Z","msg":"話時話<br />\n<br />\n條仔食咗佢係咪要結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efe92e7fde87bac5b54c02da025c7e7c8869953","tid":1180430,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20083fcb745611bba26507eb39ec9cd49db497a0","tid":1180